headline: GTA Online
subtitle: The Cayo Perico Heist
content:
Robbing the biggest bank in the country? Been there. Raiding the casino’s vaults? Done that. Infiltrating the heavily guarded private party island of the ruthless drug lord El Rubio? Now you’re talking.

Leave behind the lights of Los Santos for the sands of Cayo Perico and your biggest heist yet. All you need is the right contact and he’s waiting in the VIP section of the newest club in Los Santos, The Music Locker.
